@startuml C4_Browsing_Domain

title C4 - Browsing Domain Model

top to bottom direction
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontStyle bold
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

package "Domain" {
  enum IntegrityStatusEnum {
    VALID
    INVALID
    UNKNOWN
  }

  class Dip <<entity>> {
    +id: number
    +uuid: string
    +integrityStatus: IntegrityStatusEnum
  }

  class DocumentClass <<entity>> {
    +id: number
    +dipId: number
    +name: string
    +integrityStatus: IntegrityStatusEnum
  }

  class Process <<entity>> {
    +id: number
    +documentClassId: number
    +integrityStatus: IntegrityStatusEnum
  }

  class Document <<entity>> {
    +id: number
    +processId: number
    +integrityStatus: IntegrityStatusEnum
  }

  class File <<entity>> {
    +id: number
    +documentId: number
    +filename: string
    +path: string
    +hash: string
    +integrityStatus: IntegrityStatusEnum
  }

  class Metadata <<value-object>>
}

Dip "1" o-- "0..*" DocumentClass
DocumentClass "1" o-- "0..*" Process
Process "1" o-- "0..*" Document
Document "1" o-- "0..*" File

note right of Dip
Hierarchy used by browsing use cases:
Dip -> DocumentClass -> Process -> Document -> File
end note

@enduml
